About Awon Haider Games
Your Source for Mobile Entertainment
Welcome to Awon Haider Games, a top Game Studio in Lahore since 2020. Our talented and hardworking team is dedicated to ensuring that everything Awon Haider Games creates is cool, fun and exciting. As a rule, we’ve agreed never release anything “less than awesome”. Read on to learn more about our business, our games, and what we have to offer our community of gamers.
